ay\nthrough $\\gamma$-ray bands. With the pulse morphology of the $\\gamma$-ray\nemissions, we argue that the inclination angle and the viewing angle for the\nGeminga pulsar are $\\alpha\\sim 50^{\\circ}$ and $\\xi\\sim 90^{\\circ}$,\nrespectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Oct 2008 08:33:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
