rvations for individual objects.We also\nconsider the effect of a recently proposed correction for radiation pressure\nwhen determining black hole masses with reverberation mapping, and find that\nthe revised mass estimates do not significantly alter the range of bolometric\ncorrections seen but may yield a narrower distribution of Eddington ratios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Oct 2008 09:16:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
